      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MASTER KILCOY (4) was well backed last start but ran below expectations when fifth (20.48), beaten 7 lengths. Should bounce back. COME BACK CANDY (1) led early but gathered in and found a bit of trouble before finishing fourth (20.25) at this track over 342m in a TG1-4W. Has good speed and aided by the cherry draw. Expected to feature on best form. I'M MY DESIGN (7) has good speed and can quickly clear the draw. Last start finished 4th on March 18 over 342m at this track behind On The Strip beaten 5.5 lengths (20.41) in a TG1-4W. With even luck and a clean start can sneak into the finish. LEFEVRE GOLD (2) is a last-start placegetter from this box – sure to have admirers.",
